crabgent-tool-compact
=====================

The deterministic semantic tool-output filters in this crate (the
test-runner, git, ls, grep, read_file, and mcp output reductions) are a
clean-room native reimplementation inspired by the design of the rtk
tool, which is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

No rtk source code is included, copied, or linked. Only the
filter-design lineage is acknowledged here as an Apache-2.0 courtesy.

This crate is part of the crabgent workspace and is licensed under
"Apache-2.0 OR MIT"; see the workspace-level LICENSE-APACHE and
LICENSE-MIT files for the full terms.
